tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE evaluation_data (
  student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  intervention_id INT,
  program_name VARCHAR,
  intervention_date DATE,
  effectiveness_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Evaluation (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
student_name TEXT,
intervention_type TEXT,
effectiveness_rating INT);

CREATE TABLE ProgramData (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
program_name TEXT,
start_date DATE,
end_date DATE,
completion_status TEXT);
CREATE TABLE interventions ( intervention_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, intervention_name TEXT NOT NULL, intervention_type TEXT NOT NULL, start_date DATE NOT NULL, end_date DATE NOT NULL )
CREATE TABLE participants ( participant_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, first_name TEXT NOT NULL, last_name TEXT NOT NULL, age INT NOT NULL, gender TEXT NOT NULL )
CREATE TABLE intervention_results ( result_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, intervention_id INT NOT NULL, participant_id INT NOT NULL, effectiveness_score INT NOT NULL, feedback TEXT )

CREATE TABLE Students (
  student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  student_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  grade_level INT
);

CREATE TABLE Courses (
  course_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  course_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  instructor_id INT,
  department VARCHAR(50),
  credit_hours INT
);

CREATE TABLE Enrollments (
  enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id INT,
  course_id INT,
  enrollment_date DATE,
  grade VARCHAR(2)
);

CREATE TABLE Instructors (
  instructor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  instructor_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  department VARCHAR(50),
  experience_years INT,
  email VARCHAR(50)
);
